Package ch.epfl.lis.wingj.structure

Implements methods and objects to generate structure models of biological organisms or organs.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Boundary
    Describes a compartment boundary (XY trajectory).
    Compartment
    Describes a compartment (XY closed shape).
    DetectorWorker
    Worker thread for running structure detectors.
    Overlay
    Abstract class for implementing overlay to paint on top of the structure viewer.
    Structure
    Abstract class to extend to describe a morphological structure to identify using an extended instance of StructureDetector.
    StructureDataset
    Implements methods to save structure datasets.
    StructureDetectionModule
    Abstract class for implementing one step of the detection of a morphological structure.
    StructureDetector
    Abstract class for implementing a morphological structure detector.
    StructureSnake
    Abstract class to extend for descrbing a morphological structure using B-splines.
